Game
- show greetings
- ask user name
- save user name

- show initial message (rules, what to do)
- start game cycle
- ask question using randomizer
- wait user answer

- check answer
- if answer is correct - show correct answer message and continue game or show congrats message and finish the game
- if answer is wrong - show wrong answer message and finish the game

Game should:
- provide messages to engine
- provide questions texts
- check answers
- check continue game conditions
